# Optional AR asset overrides (Vite env vars — must be prefixed with VITE_).
# By default the MediaPipe WASM fileset and pose models load from public CDNs (cached after first
# run). Point these at self-hosted copies for an offline / faster-first-load demo. To self-host the
# WASM, copy node_modules/@mediapipe/tasks-vision/wasm into client/public/mediapipe/wasm and set:
#
# VITE_MEDIAPIPE_WASM_BASE=/mediapipe/wasm
# VITE_POSE_MODEL_FULL=/mediapipe/pose_landmarker_full.task
# VITE_POSE_MODEL_LITE=/mediapipe/pose_landmarker_lite.task
